data.description: Discover your new home for the holidays in Lakewood Estates! This 4 bedroom 2 bath home, built in 2021, combines luxury and comfort. The open concept invites festive gatherings, and custom details add a touch of elegance. Enjoy the spacious living area and sleek kitchen. The home features generously sized bedrooms with large closets. Outside, a huge yard with a privacy fence ensures a private, safe play space. Make 1431 Sundance your haven—schedule your tour today and unwrap the gift of a lifetime!
